Bullseye, who cares about tools?  The fact is Thuergist out level Sorcs with their eyes closed.  I started my Sorc the same time a friend made his Thuergist. I'm now level 23 and he's level 33.  We don't always get to play at the same times so we solo alot.  From day one I've been killing blues and yellows, he's been killing orange and some reds.   Reds are tricky for him and he uses most of his mana, but he can do them.  I've gotten so far behind I can't party with him without feeling like a leech anyway.<P>The Thuergist is probably the only class left that can still take on Orange and Red MOBS on a regular basis.  So we have more tools, they don't need them obviously, so who cares about them?
