Guys, I play a Cleric (lvl 32) and a Sorc (Lvl 16) (Cleric is my main).<P>Without hesitation, the Sorc is much MUCH better at CC.  <P>At best a Cleric can have a couple adds mezzed for like 19 seconds.  Then unless the tanks can aggro all those adds, the cleric is most likely dead, or the group is dead because he can't get any heals off.<P>To say that a cleric can do CC just as well as a Sorcerer is proposterous.<P>Now if you want to compare a Sorc to a Midgard Healer, then you have a very valid point.
